<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Conquest_of_Fadak" title="Conquest of Fadak">Fadak</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Third_Expedition_of_Wadi_al_Qura" title="Third Expedition of Wadi al Qura">Qura</a></li>
<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Expedition_of_Dhat_al-Riqa" title="Expedition of Dhat al-Riqa">Dhat</a></li>
