</section><section data-mw-section-id="38" id="mwA8w"><h2 id="Notes">Notes</h2>
<div class="reflist columns references-column-width" style="-moz-column-width: 30em; -webkit-column-width: 30em; column-width: 30em; list-style-type: decimal;" about="#mwt1957" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"reflist","href":"./Template:Reflist"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"30em"},"group":{"wt":"\"n\""}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA80">
<ol class="mw-references references" data-mw-group="n" typeof="mw:Extension/references" about="#mwt2498" data-mw='{"name":"references","attrs":{"group":"n","responsive":"0"},"body":{"html":""}}'><li about="#cite_note-1" id="cite_note-1"><a href="./Muhammad#cite_ref-1" data-mw-group="n" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-1" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Arabic_name" title="Arabic name" id="mwA84">Full name</a>: <b id="mwA88">Abū al-Qāsim Muḥammad ibn ʿAbd Allāh ibn ʿAbd al-Muṭṭalib ibn Hāšim</b> (<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Arabic_language" title="Arabic language" about="#mwt15" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"lang-ar","href":"./Template:Lang-ar"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"ابو القاسم محمد ابن عبد الله ابن عبد المطلب ابن هاشم"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA9A" class="mw-redirect">Arabic</a><span about="#mwt15" id="mwA9E">: </span><span lang="ar" dir="rtl" about="#mwt15" id="mwA9I">ابو القاسم محمد ابن عبد الله ابن عبد المطلب ابن هاشم</span><span typeof="mw:Entity" about="#mwt15" id="mwA9M">‎</span><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Articles_containing_Arabic-language_text" about="#mwt15" id="mwA9Q"/>, lit: Father of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Qasim_ibn_Muhammad" title="Qasim ibn Muhammad" id="mwA9U">Qasim</a> Muhammad son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Abdallah_ibn_Abd_al-Muttalib" title="Abdallah ibn Abd al-Muttalib" id="mwA9Y" class="mw-redirect">Abd Allah</a> son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Abd_al-Muttalib" title="Abd al-Muttalib" id="mwA9c">Abd al-Muttalib</a> son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Hashim_ibn_Abd_Manaf" title="Hashim ibn Abd Manaf" id="mwA9g">Hashim</a>)</span></li><li about="#cite_note-2" id="cite_note-2"><a href="./Muhammad#cite_ref-2" data-mw-group="n" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-2" class="mw-reference-text">Classical Arabic pronunciation</span></li><li about="#cite_note-8" id="cite_note-8"><a href="./Muhammad#cite_ref-8" data-mw-group="n" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-8" class="mw-reference-text">The <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Ahmadiyya" title="Ahmadiyya" id="mwA9k">Ahmadiyya Muslim Community</a> considers Muhammad to be the "Seal of the Prophets" (Khātam an-Nabiyyīn) and the last law-bearing Prophet but not the last Prophet. See:
<ul id="mwA9o"><li id="mwA9s"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt23" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book ","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/?id=MdRth02Q6nAC&amp;pg=PA134&amp;dq#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false"},"title":{"wt":"Islam and the Ahmadiyya Jama&apos;at: History, Belief, Practice"},"author":{"wt":"Simon Ross Valentine"},"page":{"wt":"134"},"publisher":{"wt":"Columbia University Press"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-1-85065-916-7"},"year":{"wt":"2008"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA9w">Simon Ross Valentine (2008). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/?id=MdRth02Q6nAC&amp;pg=PA134&amp;dq#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false" id="mwA90"><i id="mwA94">Islam and the Ahmadiyya Jama'at: History, Belief, Practice</i></a>. Columbia University Press. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA98"> </span>134. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwA-A">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA-E"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-1-85065-916-7" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-85065-916-7" id="mwA-I">978-1-85065-916-7</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Islam+and+the+Ahmadiyya+Jama%27at%3A+History%2C+Belief%2C+Practice&amp;rft.pages=134&amp;rft.pub=Columbia+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-85065-916-7&amp;rft.au=Simon+Ross+Valentine&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2F%3Fid%3DMdRth02Q6nAC%26pg%3DPA134%26dq%23v%3Donepage%26q%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMuhammad" class="Z3988" about="#mwt23" id="mwA-M"></span><style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r879151008" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" about="#mwt23" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwA-Q">.mw-par