posito&amp;rft.aufirst=John&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMuhammad" class="Z3988" about="#mwt20" id="mwBBc"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt20" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwBBg"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-9" id="cite_note-9"><a href="./Muhammad#cite_ref-9" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-9" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt36" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"https://www.al-islam.org/life-muhammad-prophet-sayyid-saeed-akhtar-rizvi/early-years"},"title":{"wt":"Early Years"},"website":{"wt":"Al-Islam.org"},"language":{"wt":"en"},"access-date":{"wt":"2018-10-18"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBBk"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://www.al-islam.org/life-muhammad-prophet-sayyid-saeed-akhtar-rizvi/early-years" id="mwBBo">"Early Years"</a>. <i id="mwBBs">Al-Islam.org</i><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwBBw">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwBB0">2018-10-18</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Al-Islam.org&amp;rft.atitle=Early+Years&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.al-islam.org%2Flife-muhammad-prophet-sayyid-saeed-akhtar-rizvi%2Fearly-years&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMuhammad" class="Z3988" about="#mwt36" id="mwBB4"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt36" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwBB8"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-10" id="cite_note-10"