<li id="mwBDA"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt51" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite book ","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"publisher":{"wt":"G. Bell"},"last":{"wt":"Sherrard Beaumont Burnaby"},"title":{"wt":"Elements of the Jewish and Muhammadan calendars: with rules and tables and explanatory notes on the Julian and Gregorian calendars"},"year":{"wt":"1901"},"url":{"wt":"https://archive.org/details/elementsofjewish00burnuoft"},"page":{"wt":"465"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBDE">Sherrard Beaumont Burnaby (1901). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://archive.org/details/elementsofjewish00burnuoft" id="mwBDI"><i id="mwBDM">Elements of the Jewish and Muhammadan calendars: with rules and tables and explanatory notes on the Julian and Gregorian calendars</i></a>. G. Bell. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBDQ"> </span>465.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Elements+of+the+Jewish+and+Muhammadan+calendars%3A+with+rules+and+tables+and+explanatory+notes+on+the+Julian+and+Gregorian+calendars&amp;rft.pages=465&amp;rft.pub=G.+Bell&amp;rft.date=1901&amp;rft.au=Sherrard+Beaumont+Burnaby&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Felementsofjewish00burnuoft&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMuhammad" class="Z3988" about="#mwt51" id="mwBDU"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt51" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwBDY"/></li>
