2w">Wayback Machine</a><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Webarchive_template_wayback_links" about="#mwt1235" id="mwB20"/> Book 1, Hadith 5 &amp; Book 1, Hadith 7/8</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Safi2009-232" id="cite_note-Safi2009-232"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Muhammad#cite_ref-Safi2009_232-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Muhammad#cite_ref-Safi2009_232-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Safi2009-232" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt1240" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book ","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"author":{"wt":"Omid Safi"},"title":{"wt":"Memories of Muhammad: why the Prophet matters"},"url":{"wt":"https://books.google.com/books?id=Gs2oDbagvfIC&amp;pg=PA273"},"accessdate":{"wt":"5 November 2011"},"date":{"wt":"17 November 2009"},"publisher":{"wt":"HarperCollins"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-0-06-123134-6"},"pages":{"wt":"273–274"},"deadurl":{"wt":"no"},"archiveurl":{"wt":"https://web.archive.org/web/20130615065426/http://books.google.com/books?id=Gs2oDbagvfIC&amp;pg=PA273"},"archivedate":{"wt":"15 June 2013"},"df":{"wt":"dmy-all"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwB24">Omid Safi (17 November 2009). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=Gs2oDbagvfIC&amp;pg=PA273" id="mwB28"><i id="mwB3A">Memories of Muhammad: why the Prophet matters</i></a>. HarperCollins. pp.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwB3E"> </span>273–274. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwB3I">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwB3M"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-06-123134-6" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-06-123134-6" id="mwB3Q">978-0-06-123134-6</a>. <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130615065426/http://books.google.com/