B48">Muhammad: Prophet For Our Time</i>, HarperPress, 2006, p. 105</span></li><li about="#cite_note-Haykal-244" id="cite_note-Haykal-244"><a href="./Muhammad#cite_ref-Haykal_244-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-Haykal-244" class="mw-reference-text">Muhammad Husayn Haykal, <i id="mwB5A">The Life of Muhammad</i>, North American Trust Publications (1976), p. 139</span></li><li about="#cite_note-245" id="cite_note-245"><a href="./Muhammad#cite_ref-245" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-245" class="mw-reference-text">Barlas (2002), pp. 125–26</span></li><li about="#cite_note-246" id="cite_note-246"><a href="./Muhammad#cite_ref-246" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-246" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation book" about="#mwt1294" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book ","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last1":{"wt":"A.C. Brown"},"first1":{"wt":"Jonathan"},"authorlink":{"wt":"Jonathan A.C. Brown"},"title":{"wt":"Misquoting Muhammad: The Challenge and Choices of Interpreting the Prophet&apos;s Legacy"},"date":{"wt":"2014"},"publisher":{"wt":"[[Oneworld Publications]]"},"isbn":{"wt":"978-1-78074-420-9"},"pages":{"wt":"143–44"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwB5E"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Jonathan_A.C._Brown" title="Jonathan A.C. Brown" id="mwB5I" class="mw-redirect">A.C. Brown, Jonathan</a> (2014). <i id="mwB5M">Misquoting Muhammad: The Challenge and Choices of Interpreting the Prophet's Legacy</i>. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Oneworld_Publications" title="Oneworld Publications" id="mwB5Q">Oneworld Publications</a>. pp.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwB5U"> </span>143–44. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number" id="mwB5Y">ISBN</a><span typeof=